data.description: Spacious 2 story home with an amazing yard, covered front porch and a two car detached garage. Large living room, lots of natural sunlight. Main floor also offers a Full bathroom and Side door entry area with closet- perfect for your coats & shoe collection. Updated- Eat-in-Kitchen large enough for a table and comes with an island with additional seating. 3 bedrooms upstairs with ample closet space. Unfinished basement- washer & dryer included. Interior photos will be posted soon!
